---------------------------------------------------------
|0 |SUBPLAN FILTER      |         |5       |115         |
|1 |├─TABLE FULL SCAN   |t1       |5       |3           |
|2 |└─SCALAR GROUP BY   |         |1       |23          |
|3 |  └─TABLE RANGE SCAN|t3(t1_id)|1       |23          |
=========================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
