|3 |│ └─SORT                   |                            |1       |5           |
|4 |│   └─MERGE SEMI JOIN      |                            |1       |5           |
|5 |│     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |granparent1(col_varchar_key)|1       |3           |
|6 |│     └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |c(col_varchar_key)          |2       |3           |
|7 |└─MATERIAL                 |                            |1       |3           |
|8 |  └─SUBPLAN SCAN           |VIEW3                       |1       |3           |
|9 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |parent2                     |1       |3           |
===================================================================================
